    "The strongest 20 collocates are shown in Table 5.",
    "'Has' (LogDice: 8.46688) shows a slight decrease in collocational strength but remains one of the top collocates in January 2023.",
    "Once again, there are many occasions where ChatGPT is the object of constructions as they are presented in the passive voice ('Chatgpt has been corrupted', 'Chat-GPT has been trained on data till 2021', 'ChatGPT has been overhyped').",
    "Within these examples, the subject of the construction is excluded, meaning that ChatGPT becomes the focus of the tweet despite having limited social agency.",
    "This demonstrates the further occurrence of ChatGPT disguising the human agents behind its creation and development, which may see it blamed or not trusted in the future."
